1. **Sjajne** vesti su stigle iz Beograda. (Great news have arrived from Belgrade.)
2. Ova haljina je **sjajne** boje. (This dress is of a brilliant color.)
3. Vidim da ti oči danas **sjajne**. (I can see that your eyes are sparkling today.)
4. Ona je jedna **sjajne** osobe. (She is a great person.)
5. Moramo učiniti nešto da poboljšamo **sjajnost** ovog ogledala. (We need to do something to improve the brightness of this mirror.)
6. Njegova karijera je dostigla veliku **sjajnost**. (His career has achieved great brilliance.)
7. *Sjajno* si ovo uradio! (You did this brilliantly!)
8. Molim te, obriši ove cipele **sjajnom** krpom. (Please wipe these shoes with a shiny cloth.)
9. Ovaj restoran je jedan od **najsjajnijih** u gradu. (This restaurant is one of the brightest in town.)
10. **Sjajni** predlozi koje si dao su pomogli u rešavanju problema. (The great suggestions you gave helped solve the problem.)